originalText.text: A very delayed review, but I cant thank the team enough for the amazing service they provided in obtaining my E3 visa twice. Employees are approachable, timely in communication and responsive to questions (even when I asked the same ones multiple times!) They make the whole visa process which can be anxiety inducing, smooth and as easy as possible. I will be heading back for my next visa application. I cannot recommend them enough! Thank you!

originalText.text: Cammisa Markel assisted me throughout the process of obtaining my E3 visa. From start to finish the experience with the firm was faultless. Both Sharla & Emily were quick to answer any questions and were extremely helpful when doing so. Every bit of paperwork was produced perfectly and no stone was left unturned. This meant I could turn up to my interview with a level of confidence I certainly would not have had in the absence of their prep work. Can't thank you enough!

originalText.text:
The team at Cammisa Markel made my E3 visa application process so incredibly seamless and stress free!
It was very straight forward, easy, and a very quick turn around in all aspects of the process!

A very special shout out to Sarah F who is an absolute star and made me feel so comfortable during this time! Incredible communication and a breath of fresh air :)

So appreciative for all of their help and work and can highly recommend them to anyone looking for help with their application!

Thank you, team!!
